  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a large cast-iron skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add diced onion and cook until translucent, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add minced garlic and cook for an additional 1 minute.",
    "Add diced sweet potato, Jamaican scotch bonnet peppers, allspice berries, and salt. Cook for 5-6 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add Saskatoon berries, dark soy sauce, and a pinch of salt. Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes, stirring frequently.",
    "Create 2 wells in the mixture and crack in the beaten eggs. Cook until the eggs are set.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh cilantro and serve immediately."
  ],
